data.description: This cute 3 bedroom 1 1/2 bath with basement is ready for you to move in. This all brick home sits on a .20 acre fenced lot. When you walk in you will find a spacious living room. The living room opens up to the eat in kitchen. Down the hall you find 3 bedrooms, a full bath and a half bath. The basement has a finished bonus room that can be used for a rec room or office - the possibilities are endless. There is also a large utility room with washer and dryer included and unfinished space that could easily be finished. There is a one car garage and a large fenced back yard. Call your favorite agent to see this property today. Professional photos coming soon.
